                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="fc_3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionone">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <hr>
                                <div class="accordion_item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header accordion_btn collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#fc_4">
                                        Which Helperland professional will come to my place?

                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="fc_4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionone">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <hr>
                                <div class="accordion_item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header accordion_btn collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#fc_5">
                                        Which Helperland professional will come to my place?

                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="fc_5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionone">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <hr>
                                <div class="accordion_item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header accordion_btn collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#fc_6">
                                        Which Helperland professional will come to my place?

                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="fc_6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionone">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <hr>
                                <div class="help">
                                    <p><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Faq" style=" text-decoration: none; color: #1D7A8C;">For more help</a></p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <!--question code end-->

            </div>
            <!--rightside code end-->
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--middle code end-->
    <!-- javascript code start-->
    <script src="~/Javascript/Bookservice.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Javascript/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Javascript/main.js"></script>
    <!--javasrcipt code end-->

</body>
</html>
